This  brand new  unused apartment is a semi-furnished unit with a super built-up area of 875 sq. ft. It is located in a newly constructed building (gated society) situated at a peaceful and urban neighbourhood of Panchasayar, near New Garia Metro Station and E. M. Bypass.

In addition to that, you also get the convenience of your own covered car parking spot with an area of 135 sq. ft.


Furnishings :

Immaculately designed interiors in contemporary style, this semi-furnished apartment comes with  all new  furniture items (10), collapsible gate, balcony box grill, window box grill, wall colors, curtains, lighting, false ceiling (3), decoration, etc. The apartment bestows luxury and quality, fitted with branded items like, Jaquar bath fittings, Kajaria vitrified tiles, Crabtree electricals, Philips lighting, Asian Paints Royale Play wall colors and much more.

The property is under Ward No. 109 of Kolkata Municipal Corporation (KMC) and gets electricity supply from CESC.

The apartment is Feng Shui / Vaastu Compliant.
